15:T409,Internal brochure evidence clearly defines this as a surgical positioning instrument component specifically designed to secure the non-operative leg during anterior approach hip replacement surgery. The device attaches to OR table side rails and provides adjustable leg positioning through an extension rail/deck system with ball heel slider mechanism. External sources confirm Meril manufactures orthopedic instruments but provide no specific information about this product. Classification as 'instrument' under 'Positioning Systems' category is clinically accurate. High confidence in semantic meaning, but brand absence and lack of external verification warrants review to: (1) confirm this is a Meril-manufactured product vs. third-party OR table accessory, (2) determine if part of a larger positioning system family, (3) verify product naming convention. Material specification as medical grade metals is appropriate for OR table mounting hardware. No conflicts detected between internal description and product classification.7:["$","div",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#0A0A0A] text-white","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org/\",\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"Opposite Leg Holder (OLH)\",\"description\":\"A component designed to hold the non-operative leg during anterior hip replacement procedures. Attaches to OR table side rails and includes an extension rail and deck system with adjustable leg length positioning.\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"Meril\"},\"category\":\"Positioning Systems\",\"manufacturer\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Meril Life Sciences\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateOffer\",\"offerCount\":\"1\",\"lowPrice\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"INR\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\"}}"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-24","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"fle